def momentum_GD(x,y,alpha,epochs,gama):  
    theta_0=[]
    theta_1=[]
    ress=[]
    theta0=0
    theta1=0
    hyp=[]
    v0=0
    v1=0
    v_0=[]
    v_1=[]

    for i in range(epochs):
        h=theta0+theta1*x
        hyp.append(h)
        error = sum((h-y)**2)
        res = error/ (2 * len(x))
        ress.append(res)
        a = sum(h-y) / ( len(x))
        b = sum((h-y)*x) / ( len(x))
        
        v0=gama*v0+ (alpha*a)
        v_0.append(v0)
        theta0 = theta0 - v0
        theta_0.append(theta0)
        v1=gama*v1+ (alpha*b)
        theta1 = theta1 - v1
        theta_1.append(theta1)
        v_1.append(v1)
        if i>0 and abs(ress[-1]-ress[-2])< 0.001 : 
            break
    dict1={"theta_0":theta0,"theta_1":theta1,"losses":ress,"hypothesis output":hyp,"optimum theta_0":theta_0,"optimum theta_1":theta_1}
    return dict1

def momentum_GD(x,y,alpha,epochs,gama):  
    theta_0=[]
    theta_1=[]
    ress=[]
    theta0=0
    theta1=0
    hyp=[]
    v0=0
    v1=0
    v_0=[]
    v_1=[]

    for i in range(epochs):
        h=theta0+theta1*x
        hyp.append(h)
        error = sum((h-y)**2)
        res = error/ (2 * len(x))
        ress.append(res)
        a = sum(h-y) / ( len(x))
        b = sum((h-y)*x) / ( len(x))
        
        v0=gama*v0+ (alpha*a)
        v_0.append(v0)
        theta0 = theta0 - v0
        theta_0.append(theta0)
        v1=gama*v1+ (alpha*b)
        theta1 = theta1 - v1
        theta_1.append(theta1)

        if i>0 and abs(ress[-1]-ress[-2])< 0.001 : 
            break
    dict1={"theta_0":theta0,"theta_1":theta1,"losses":ress,"hypothesis output":hyp,"optimum theta_0":theta_0,"optimum theta_1":theta_1}
    return dict1

def NAG_GD(x,y,alpha,epochs,gama):  
    theta_0=[]
    theta_1=[]
    ress=[]
    loss=[]
    theta0=0
    theta0temp=0
    theta1=0
    theta1temp=0
    hyp=[]
    hyt=[]
    v0=0
    v1=0
    v_0=[]
    v_1=[]
    v_0_temp=[]
    v_1_temp=[]
    v0t=0
    v1t=0
    theta1_temp=[]
    theta0_temp=[]
    for i in range(epochs):
        h=theta0+theta1*x
        hyp.append(h)
        
        htemp=theta0temp+theta1temp*x
        hyt.append(htemp)
        
        error = sum((h-y)**2)
        res = error/ (2 * len(x))
        ress.append(res)
        
        error1 = sum((htemp-y)**2)
        les = error1/ (2 * len(x))
        loss.append(les)
        
        a = sum(h-y) / ( len(x))
        b = sum((h-y)*x) / ( len(x))
        
        atemp = sum(htemp-y) / ( len(x))
        btemp = sum((htemp-y)*x) / ( len(x))
        
        v0=gama*v0+ (alpha*a)
        
        v0t=gama*v0+ (alpha*atemp)
        
        v_0_temp.append(v0t)
        v_0.append(v0)
 

        theta0temp = theta0 - gama*v0
        theta0_temp.append(theta0temp)
                
        theta0 = theta0temp - alpha *atemp
        theta_0.append(theta0)

        v1=gama*v1+ (alpha*b)
        v1t=gama*v1+ (alpha*btemp)
        v_1_temp.append(v1t)
        
        theta1temp = theta1 - gama*v1
        theta1_temp.append(theta1temp)
        
        
        theta1 = theta1temp - alpha *atemp
        theta_1.append(theta1)
        
        v_1.append(v1)
        if i>0 and abs(ress[-1]-ress[-2])< 0.001 : 
            break
    dict1={"theta_0":theta0,"theta_1":theta1, "theta0temp" : theta0temp , "theta1temp":theta1temp , "losses":ress ,"losstemp":loss ,"hypothesis output":hyp, "htemp":htemp,"optimum theta_0":theta_0,"optimum theta_1":theta_1,"theta0temp":theta0_temp,"theta1temp":theta0_temp}
    return dict1
